            "last_activity_date": 1493026098,
            "creation_date": 1493026098,
            "body": "<p>Try to use Shared Preference, declare it in your onCreate Method.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>SharedPreferences sharedPref = \ngetActivity().getPreferences(Context.MODE_PRIVATE);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Read the Boolean variable in onCreate method of your second Activity.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Boolean highScore = sharedPref.getBoolean(\"show\", true);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Save the Boolean variable that stores whether the buttons should show or not<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Boolean show = false; // Controlled by your button events\n\nSharedPreferences.Editor editor = sharedPref.edit();\neditor.putBoolean(\"show\", show);\neditor.commit();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 43584422,
            "question_id": 43584126
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/37b6db73a028e7dd0140206b21c1a18a?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
                "account_id": 10754398,
